<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261199>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Preserved specimens, dorsal view. A, Pachycheles monilifer (Dana, 1852), ovigerous female (MZUSP- 10596); B, Pachycheles riisei (Stimpson, 1859), ovigerous female (DOUFPE- 7485); C, Pachycheles rugimanus A. Milne-Edwards, 1880, male (USNM- 188445); D, Petrolisthes amoenus (Guérin-Menéville, 1855), ovigerous female (MZUSP- 16713); E, Petrolisthes armatus (Gibbes, 1850), male (MZUSP- 20173); F, Petrolisthes galathinus (Bosc, 1802), ovigerous female (MZUSP- 11303); G, Petrolisthes marginatus Stimpson, 1858, ovigerous female (MNRJ- 3635); H, Petrolisthes rosariensis Werding, 1978, male (MZUSP- 10713). Scales: A, C – H (5 mm); B (1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261199/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

